title: Grateful Dead - Postcards of the Hanging [FLAC]
description:
http://i.imgur.com/RdCHFVH.jpg



Grateful Dead - Postcards of the Hanging - Grateful Dead Perform the Songs of Bob Dylan (2002) [FLAC]



1. When I Paint My Masterpiece - October 11, 1989 at Meadowlands Arena in East Rutherford, NJ
2. She Belongs to Me - September 15, 1985 in Chula Vista, CA
3. Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues - July 12, 1989 at RFK Stadium in Washington, DC
4. Maggie's Farm - October 3, 1987 at Shoreline Amphitheater in Mountain View, CA
5. Stuck Inside of Mobile with the Memphis Blues Again - July 16, 1988 at The Greek Theater, Berkeley, CA
6. It Takes a Lot to Laugh, It Takes a Train to Cry - June 10, 1973 at RFK Stadium in Washington, DC
7. Ballad of a Thin Man - April 1, 1988 at Meadowlands Arena in East Rutherford, NJ
8. Desolation Row - March 24, 1990 at The Knickerbocker Arena in Albany, NY
9. All Along the Watchtower - July 4, 1989 at Rich Stadium, Orchard Park, NY
10. It's All Over Now, Baby Blue - December 3, 1981 at Dane County Coliseum in Madison,WI
11. Man of Peace - June 9, 1987 (Rehearsal for Dylan & The Dead summer tour) in San Rafael, CA


Jerry Garcia - lead guitar, vocals
Bob Weir - rhythm guitar, vocals
Phil Lesh - bass guitar, vocals
Brent Mydland - keyboards, organ, vocals (except track 6)
Mickey Hart - drums
Bill Kreutzmann - drums
Keith Godchaux - piano (track 6)

Dickey Betts - guitar (track 6)
Bob Dylan - acoustic guitar, vocals (track 11)
Butch Trucks - drums (track 6)
